{"title":"焦裕禄","authors":["林林"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":5,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦裕禄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坟头有老农们在痛哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为好人早死哀恸万分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墓中人深知民间疾苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村民爱他因为他爱村民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泡桐树变沙丘为绿土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他驱逐穷鬼饿鬼像神明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是大公无私的公仆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有颗鞠躬尽瘁高贵的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是当之无愧的楷模，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应当把这面明镜高悬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对照自己是何等干部？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众在呼唤焦裕禄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来领导能否青出于蓝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为民造福走康庄大路？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}